the info you pasted
you only have 1 active queue, which means that all 3 of your remaining urls
are on the same host. Most likely your crawl is in the slow retry cycle
because that particular host is not responding. You probably have crawled
everything you really want by that point and can

terminate the crawl manually.
See
https://webarchive.jira.com/wiki/display/Heritrix/unexpectedly+slow+crawling+on+idle+crawler

